snippet.title: Boss 101 Xbox One Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Join STEVE and Max as they battle against Boss 101 and save the galaxy.

During your journey you will battle bosses you created with the Make-A-Boss generator. You engage in combat, chase and missions to rescue baby robo-AI's from the clutches of the biggest baddie of all, the dreaded Boss 101.
